sbs-braille-tables NEWS -- history of user-visible changes.  	-*- org -*-

* Noteworthy changes in release 1.14 (2021-03-22)
** Drop gnulib
- Wasn't really needed, we can manually change the version string
** Upgrade to liblouis 3.17
- Migrate ~nocross~ to ~nocross always~
- make use of the extended ~nocross~ possibilities
- add test cases for the rules that have been upgraded to work with
  ~nocross~

* Noteworthy changes in release 1.2 (2011-02-14)
    - Improve tables

* Noteworthy changes in release 1.1 (2010-07-14) [beta]
    - Add git-version-gen
    - Add do-release-commit-and-tag

* Noteworthy changes in release 1.0.9
    - Update whitelists

* Noteworthy changes in release 1.0.8
